album.title: Deleted Scenes From The Cutting Room Floor

wiki.content: 'That Man' was indirectly the inspiration for the jingle associated with Tourism Tasmania's highly successful 'Go Behind The Scenery' campaign promoted by a video played across hundreds of venues in Australia during early and mid 2013. The bouncy, catchy and instantly likable track made the creative team behind the advertisement think 'that is how we want our soundtrack to sound'. You can view the video here - http://youtu.be/eziM99bFSj0 User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
